history of Mexico in the context

00:45:51.300 --> 00:45:54.600
of the Americas in the world,
in particular the history

00:45:54.600 --> 00:45:57.640
of popular communities as
they engaged, colonial rule

00:45:57.640 --> 00:45:59.890
and early capitalism,
national states

00:45:59.890 --> 00:46:03.380
and industrial challenges, as
well as revolutionary promises

00:46:03.380 --> 00:46:05.030
and national developments.

00:46:05.030 --> 00:46:07.910
He's the author of many
journal articles, book chapters

00:46:07.910 --> 00:46:10.760
