00:46:22.590 --> 00:46:24.650
and Spanish North
America" published

00:46:24.650 --> 00:46:27.090
by Duke University
Press in 2011.

00:46:27.090 --> 00:46:29.840
And "The Mexican Heartland: How
Communities Shaped Capitalism,

00:46:29.840 --> 00:46:33.210
a Nation, and World
History, 1500 to 2000",

00:46:33.210 --> 00:46:35.190
published by Princeton
this year.

00:46:35.190 --> 00:46:38.200
The title of his talk
today is, "An Old Regime

00:46:38.200 --> 00:46:42.960
and a New Economy: A Dynamic
Balance in Spanish Mesoamerica".

