00:47:14.170 --> 00:47:17.300
to colononizacion
de lo imaginario,

00:47:17.300 --> 00:47:18.960
to "The Eagle and the Dragon".

00:47:18.960 --> 00:47:23.550
I can just I have learned
so much and more important,

00:47:23.550 --> 00:47:27.510
always been set to
new ways of thinking.

00:47:27.510 --> 00:47:32.790
Early on, he and I focused I
want to say in different ways

00:47:32.790 --> 00:47:35.120
but on social-cultural
encounters

00:47:35.120 --> 00:47:36.960
in the Mesoamerican core.

00:47:36.960 --> 00:47:41.800
More recently, we both
turned to Spain's empire

00:47:41.800 --> 00:47:45.210
and its global role,
again, in different ways.

00:47:45.210 --> 00:47:48.300
And I want to say
exactly as it should be.

00:47:48.300 --> 00:47:50.020
How dull life would be

00:47:50.020 --> 00:47:54.230
