00:47:58.950 --> 00:48:03.130
First, I wanted to build on one
of the concepts I most admire

00:48:03.130 --> 00:48:07.320
in Serge's work, the
notion of hybridity.

00:48:07.320 --> 00:48:11.220
And second, I wanted to take
the chance to offer a preview

00:48:11.220 --> 00:48:15.560
