00:48:31.980 --> 00:48:37.980
economy, Spanish
Mesoamerica from 1550 to 1800.

00:48:37.980 --> 00:48:40.950
And this comes out of the
fact that I am in the process

00:48:40.950 --> 00:48:42.890
of completing two things.

00:48:42.890 --> 00:48:47.580
In fact, while "The Mexican
