00:48:59.040 --> 00:49:01.290
And because I have the
copyedited manuscript

00:49:01.290 --> 00:49:04.490
in front me, if you straight
me out on something pivotal,

00:49:04.490 --> 00:49:07.400
I still have time to tinker.

