of Catholic action.

01:22:35.910 --> 01:22:37.210
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

01:22:37.210 --> 01:22:38.510
&gt;&gt; Garry Sparks: And trying to
break the sort of political--

01:22:38.510 --> 01:22:39.810
